reviewText: My 2 year old daughter LOVES Dora.  She watches this DVD every day, several times a day.  If you have a Dora Addict at home, he/she will love this one.  I hear my daughter say, Mommie Dora, i say "Oh Man!" LOL.  Great disc.
It plays perfectly and my son was thrilled to get it which was just as imprtant, so I'm very pleased
very festive with lots of songs and dancing.  quickly became a favorite of my three yr old and a great addition to her dora collection
My 3 year old granddauaghter just loves Dora, It's a good learning tool as well; because she sings along, she dances, and it  teaches her to speak two languages. Dora is a good play mate.
Thank you it's in great condition. My daughter loves it she could watch it over and over and still love it each time. It came within the time limit.
This was a really great DVD. My daughter really loves it. It has three great episodes. It was brand new and in good condition just like it was described.
My daughter loves her movie! It got here fast, which really wasn't needed sense it was wrapped for her birthday several months later, but it definately did the trick!
I run a daycare and all my kids love Dora. It Is a great educational show to watch on a cold and rainy day. This was a great buy.
As with any Dora dvd my daughter absolutely loves it. You can't go wrong if you have a dora fan.

This is one of the Dora DVD's Kiersten got for a birthday present in September. She seems to like it,especially the episode with the trucks. She likes to interact with the tape(pointing out the various objects,Doing the Swiper,No Swiping.etc)We have seen all these episodes on the Dora TV show,but she doesn't seem to mind watching them again.

My Grandchildren love this dvd. They watch it over and over and over and that's not an exageration (that's in one day). They bring it to our house when they come to stay and we watch it time and time again. They interact with it. My Granddaughter is only 2 years old and she can follow the whole dvd. I's been a great teaching aid for both of them.
It came without plastic covering and had finger prints all over it. Came in grainy on my TV.
Fun and entertaining.  My 3 year old daughter walks around the house making silly faces like Dora and Boots do in this DVD.  A fun learning and entertainment DVD.
My son is loving his DVDS. I will buy more if I have to.
Great video. My son really loves Dora videos. He really enjoys watching this one.
great dvd
My three year old daughter loves Dora and really enjoyed this product.
my grandaughter loved these she plays them over and over again really glad i bought them for her thank you

she almost watches that ever day! It makes her have a lot of fun!  I'll buy some more for her in the future.
Very fun to dance along with and helps children learn how to enjoy a party instead of fearing the party.
